column2: SELECT za.SpecObjID, za.z, zi.e_bv_sfd, (po.petroMag_r - po.extinction_r) as dered_petro_r  FROM SpecObjAll AS za   JOIN PhotoObjAll AS po ON (po.objID = za.bestObjID)   JOIN Photoz AS zp ON (zp.objID = za.bestObjID)   JOIN galSpecInfo AS zi ON (zi.SpecObjID = za.specObjID)    WHERE    za.z > # AND za.zWarning = #    AND za.targetType = &&& AND za.survey = &&&    AND za.class = &&& AND zi.primtarget >= #    AND po.clean = # AND po.insideMask = #    AND dered_petro_r <= #
